title: Kids Adorably Answer Questions About Presidential Candidates
text:
“What You Missed”: Jimmy Kimmel sat down with some kids to find out what the next generation knows about the presidential candidates. The kids had a hard time recognizing the politicians, but that didn’t stop them from giving answers… super adorab
